data.description: Welcome yourself to your new home in Rocking K's only gated community. This 2021 Lennar Acacia II floor plan features upgrades galore. Spacious 5 bed, 3 full bath with Lennar's top tier luxury flooring, kitchen & bathroom packages on a premium lot - only home in the cul-de-sac with no north side neighbor... all located in the desirable Rocking K community & Vail School District. One bedroom & full bath downstairs will help make hosting guests very comfortable. Upstairs has a large loft for your entertainment needs, master bedroom with large walk-in shower & closet, plus 3 more bedrooms & bath. Rocking K community features large parks with playgrounds, pickle ball & basketball courts, splash pad, & more. Don't forget to enjoy the beautiful sunrise over the Rincon mountains every morning!
